      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of the high-revving S54 platform, offering a pure analog driving experience. It features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The engine bay is immaculate, showcasing the individual throttle bodies and a perfectly functioning double-VANOS system. All mechanical tolerances are strictly within factory specifications; the vehicle has undergone a recent valve adjustment and features a reinforced rear subframe to ensure long-term structural rigidity. The chassis dynamics remain razor-sharp, with the suspension and bushings showing zero signs of fatigue. This is a collector-quality vehicle with a documented service history, original paint depth, and flawless aesthetic presentation.",
